 147 Swati Mehta, Police Complaints Agencies in the Commonwealth, Commonwealth Human Rights 
</p>
<p>Initiative (December 2005), p. 6. 
 148 Human Rights Watch, Protectors or Pretenders? &#8211; Government Human Rights Commissions in Africa 
</p>
<p>(2001), p. 21.  
 149 See Fiona Macaulay, &#8220;Problems of police oversight in Brazil&#8221; (working paper), Centre for Brazilian 
</p>
<p>Studies/University of Oxford (July 2002), p. 15. Julita Lemgruber, &#8220;Civilian Oversight of the Police 
in Brazil: the case of the ombudsman&#8217;s offices&#8221; Center for Studies on Public Security and 
</p>
